conversation.content: You are a helpful assistant with access to travel booking tools. You can help users book trips by calling separate tools for each piece of information. Use set-destination, set-dates, and set-travelers tools as the user provides information, then call confirm-booking when all information is collected. Be conversational and guide the user through the booking process.
Great! Let's get started on booking your trip. First, could you please tell me where you'd like to go?
{"success":true,"message":"Destination set to Paris","currentBooking":{"destination":"Paris"},"nextSteps":["Set travel dates using set-dates tool","Set number of travelers using set-travelers tool"]}
I've set your destination to Paris. Next, could you please tell me the dates you're planning to travel? For example, "June 1-5, 2024".
{"success":true,"message":"Travel dates set to June 1-30, 2026","currentBooking":{"destination":"Paris","dates":"June 1-30, 2026"},"nextSteps":["Set number of travelers using set-travelers tool"]}
I've updated the travel dates to June 1-30, 2026. Now, could you please let me know how many travelers will be joining this trip? Please enter a number between 1 and 10.
{"success":true,"message":"Number of travelers set to 3","currentBooking":{"destination":"Paris","dates":"June 1-30, 2026","travelers":3},"nextSteps":["Confirm booking using confirm-booking tool"]}

I've confirmed that there will be 3 travelers joining the trip. 

Now, let's finalize your booking. I'll go ahead and confirm everything for you.

Proceeding to confirm the booking...

{"success":true,"booking":{"destination":"Paris","dates":"June 1-30, 2026","travelers":3,"confirmationId":"BK-1763866646187"},"message":"Successfully booked trip to Paris for 3 traveler(s) on June 1-30, 2026"}

Your trip to Paris for 3 travelers from June 1-30, 2026, has been successfully booked! You can use the confirmation ID BK-1763866646187 for any future reference.

Is there anything else you need help with?
